    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "ALL CIRCLES ARE 6 FEET IN DIAMETER -- CENTER SPACE MAY VARY WITH ABILITY.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "All players must remain in their circle until SAUCER is airborne.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "The game begins with the Filer (A) attempting to sail the SAUCER around the HECKLERS in the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "circles (B) and (C) so that his partner in the Receiver's circle (D) can catch it.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Filer (A) must remain in his circle when serving the SAUCER.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "HECKLER (B) must remain in his circle at all times while his team is defensive. He may at-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "tempt to stop the flight of the SAUCER, or distract the Filer in any manner. Should he step",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "or fall out of his circle, his team forfeits 1 point and the offensive team retains serve.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "HECKLER (C) remains in his circle until SAUCER is airborne. He may then leave his circle to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "heckle the Receiver (D) in any manner so long as he doesn't interfere with flight of SAUCER",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "or touch the Receiver, or step into the Receiver's circle. Hecklers forfeit 2 points for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "each infraction.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "Receiver (D) attempts to catch the SAUCER in his circle. Should he do so, then his team re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "ceives 2 points. Should it be necessary for the Receiver to leave his circle to catch the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "SAUCER, then his team scores but 1 point. Should he drop or miss the SAUCER, no points are",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "scored, and the teams change positions. (A) changes with (B) and (C) changes with (D).",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "(C) is now the Filer, and (B) the Receiver. HECKLER (D) must remain in his circle, and the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "HECKLER (A) becomes the roving HECKLER.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "Teams change positions when the Receiver fails to catch the SAUCER.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "In the event that no Referee is available, disputes will be settled by mutual agreement, or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "the flip of a coin.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "status": "blank"
    },
